Russia Will Supply Japan With More Coal, Barclays Capital Says

-- B y   A l i s t a i r   H o l l o w a y
-- 
2011-03-15T16:47:22Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-15/russia-will-supply-japan-with-more-coal-barclays-capital-says.html
Amrita Sen, a London-based analyst
with  Barclays Capital , comments on the coal market after  Japan 
suffered an earthquake on March 11 and subsequent tsunami,
causing explosions at nuclear reactors. She spoke by phone
today.  “The implication is Russia will have to supply more to the
Japanese,” she said, referring to coal.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Alistair Holloway in  London  at 
 aholloway1@bloomberg.net .  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Claudia Carpenter at 
 ccarpenter2@bloomberg.net . 